      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant body damage, including large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on several panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components are non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention due to a persistent oil leak and a failing transmission that slips between gears. It will likely need to be towed or undergo major repairs before it can be considered a reliable daily driver.",
